reviewText: This trading spaces dvd was awesome.
I had only heard about this show; had never watched an episode.  These were chosen after reviewing reviews, and I am very happy to own them.  They are worth the price, very enjoyable.
Love that full episodes are included!

this dvd gives you a variety of ideas...depending on what style you are looking for.  The carribean kitchen was an unbelievable transformation....and if you like that style it was great.  From modern to different color schemes it is quite interesting and they are fun to watch.

if you plan to redue your kitchen this dvd may or may not help in your redesign in your kitchen. upon watching this dvd for ideas to do to my kitchen  it did not help. i came up with ideas on my own. it was not worth to money in my mind to even purchase this dvd. if you are a fan of trading spaces and you wish to own this dvd then feel free to purchase this dvd. i think it was a good idea at the time but wish they would have maybe give a few more ideas.
If you want to watch the show six times, this ones for you.  I enjoyed watching the new ideas unfold.  Six shows for ten bucks!  What a deal!
